data.description: NEW ROOF / 1,368 SQ FT.  Introducing 5735 Mosaic Drive, Holiday, FL 34690 - a slice of paradise along the Anclote River. This lovely 2-bedroom, 2.5-bath home with a spacious 2-car garage offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. Inside, you'll find stainless steel appliances in the kitchen and easy maintenance tile floors throughout. At 1368 sq ft, this corner lot gem boasts plenty of room to relax. But what truly sets this home apart is the lifestyle it offers. With a new roof, fresh paint inside and out, and a new privacy fence, it's practically maintenance-free. A big fully fenced in yard with a gate for your toys, so you can fully savor the outdoor space without the work.  With a large Florida room that can be used as a third bedroom or office there's plenty of space for guests. Now, let's talk about the neighborhood. Holiday, Florida, is a charming riverside town known for its picturesque waterfront, including the Anclote River. Enjoy boating, fishing, and serene walks by the river. The area is dotted with local shops, parks, and friendly neighbors, making it a wonderful place to call home. And the beach is just minutes away. 5735 Mosaic Drive is more than a house; it's an invitation to a relaxed, riverside lifestyle. Seller is motivated,  so bring your offer! Don't miss the chance to make it your own.
